name: Harvey Spinks
bio:
Harvey's father was a programmer, and he was always fascinated by what his father did. As he grew up, that fascination turned into interest. Then that turned into motivation, then into drive, and now he'd love nothing more than to program as a living. 

 Since then, Harvey has become a goal-oriented, performance-focused, and innovative professional hungry to jump into the field and show the world what he's capable of!
